data.description: SELLER is MOTIVATED and is offering $10,000 in concessions toward rate buydown or down payment assistance. Mountain home in Colorado for sale! 3 bed, 2 bath home on 2.91 acres in Wetmore, Colorado. the property is adjacent to hundreds of acres of national forest AND a creek runs through the property! The home features a NEW water heater, NEW furnace, NEWLY sanded and stained hardwood floors, FRESH paint and more! There's plenty of room to expand in the well insulated, full unfinished basement with bath already roughed in and wood-burning stove for additional comfort. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of mountain living with hiking trails, zip line, and more. Your dream home awaits in this idyllic Colorado setting. Great LOCATION less than 30 minutes from Canon City, Pueblo, or Westcliffe, Colorado and only 15 minutes from Florence, Colorado.
